{"article_id":"301vC5tpUx2Od2pp","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The third woman","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"to accuse Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh of sexual misconduct","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"dating to his teenage years","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"described him as a `` mean drunk ''","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"who pushed `` girls against walls '' during her first televised interview .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Speaking to NBC News ' Kate Snow in an interview","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"that aired Monday night on MSNBC ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Julie Swetnick also called Kavanaugh a `` liar ''","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"for dismissing her allegations against him .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"In a sworn statement","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"signed under penalty of perjury","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"and released last week through her attorney , Michael Avenatti ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Swetnick alleged","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Kavanaugh preyed on young women .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"In Monday 's interview , Swetnick did not accuse Kavanaugh of assaulting her .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"More :","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"Brett Kavanaugh was 'belligerent and aggressive ' drinker ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Yale classmate says","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"Related :","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Brett Kavanaugh lied under oath ,","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Sen. Patrick Leahy says .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"And he showed some evidence","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"to prove it .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Swetnick also strayed at times from her sworn statement during the sitdown interview ,","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"admitting","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"she did n't know","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"if Kavanaugh and his friend at the time , Mark Judge , would `` spike '' the punch at house parties in the early 1980s","depth":14},{"id":27,"text":"`` so as to cause girls to lose their inhibitions and their ability","depth":15},{"id":28,"text":"to say 'no , ' ''","depth":15},{"id":29,"text":"an explosive allegation","depth":14},{"id":30,"text":"made in her three-page statement .","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"\" He was very aggressive .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"Very sloppy drunk .","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"A mean drunk .","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"I saw him go up to girls","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"and paw on them","depth":15},{"id":36,"text":"and try to ,","depth":16},{"id":37,"text":"you know ,","depth":18},{"id":38,"text":"get a little too handsy","depth":18},{"id":39,"text":"touching them on private parts .","depth":17},{"id":40,"text":"I saw him try to shift clothing , \"","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"Swetnick said during the television interview .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"\" I saw him push girls against walls .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"He would pretend to stumble","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"and stumble into them","depth":15},{"id":45,"text":"and knock them against walls .","depth":15},{"id":46,"text":"He would push his body against hers . \"","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"Kavanaugh has labeled Swetnick 's allegations as `` ridiculous '' and `` from the Twilight Zone .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"During the interview , Snow played a portion of Kavanaugh 's hearing from last week for Swetnick","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"during which he told the Senate Judiciary Committee","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"that there was no truth to the allegations","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"made against him by Christine Blasey Ford , Deborah Ramirez and Swetnick .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"After hearing his statement ,","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"Swetnick shook her head","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"and said ,","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"`` He 's a liar . ''","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"NBC News could not to confirm Swetnick ' s allegations .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"Of four people","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"she named","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"attending the parties ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"one said","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"he didn ' t recall ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"another was dead","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"and two others didn ' t respond .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Two days before he released Swetnick 's name and sworn statement ,","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"Avenatti told reporters in Los Angeles","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"that his client had multiple witnesses","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"to corroborate her story","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"and called her `` 100 percent credible . ''","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"In her sworn statement , Swetnick , 55 , alleged","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"Kavanaugh was among a group of boys","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"who would doctor the punch at parties","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"to `` cause girls to become inebriated and disoriented","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"so they could then be 'gang raped ' in a side room or bedroom by a 'train ' of numerous boys . ''","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"When asked by Snow","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"if she had witnessed Kavanaugh spike drinks , however ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"Swetnick said only","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"that she saw him `` around the punch containers ''","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"and had seen him `` giving red cups to quite a few girls during that time frame . ''","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"`` I do n't know","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"what he did , ''","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"she added .","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"`` But I saw him by them , yes . ''","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"In her written statement , Swetnick said","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"she had `` a firm recollection","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"of seeing boys ''","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"- including Kavanaugh -","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"`` lined up outside rooms at many of these parties","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"waiting for their 'turn ' with a girl inside the room . ''","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"More :","depth":4},{"id":90,"text":"Here are the five allegations","depth":5},{"id":91,"text":"made against Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh","depth":5},{"id":92,"text":"But , in her interview with Snow , Swetnick said","depth":5},{"id":93,"text":"the boys were not `` lined up ''","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"but `` huddled by the doors . ''","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"At the party","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"in which she said","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"he was sexually assaulted -","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"`` My body was violated .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"My soul was broken , ''","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"she told Snow -","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"Swetnick said","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"she could n't single out Kavanaugh as one of her attackers .","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"\" I can not specifically say","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"that he was one of the ones","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"who assaulted me , \"","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"Swetnick said .","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"Swetnick said","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"she told her mother","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"and reported the incident to Montgomery County police .","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"Her mother and the police officer","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"who took the report","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"are both dead ,","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"and the department told NBC News","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"it could take weeks to retrieve records about the incident .","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"President Donald Trump has remained supportive of his Supreme Court pick ,","depth":3},{"id":116,"text":"telling reporters on Monday","depth":4},{"id":117,"text":"that he believed","depth":5},{"id":118,"text":"the ongoing FBI investigation into Kavanaugh 's background would be `` a good thing . ''","depth":5},{"id":119,"text":"Also Monday , Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell said","depth":3},{"id":120,"text":"the full Senate would vote on Kavanaugh 's nomina